metadata.name: KaleiDoscope
metadata.description:
In those moments when love is made, there is endless possibility for beauty. From a simple sharing of self with other(s), there is the chance of an infinite universe fully realized in its awe inspiring grace and majesty.  
See what you want in this. May it bring you what you need, be that a knowing smile or the spark of hope.  

Holders will receive free air drops of future works and customizable files, allowing them to express themselves however they see fit. Also planned for the collection are token gated community events and raffles for signed limited edition prints.

Burn dynamics will also be utilized for future parts of the collection, including a planned Profile Pic (PP?) release.
